<table><tr><td>American Society of Anesthesiologists Task Force on Perioperative Blood Management. Practice guidelines for perioperative blood management: an updated report by the American Society of Anesthesiologists Task Force on Perioperative Blood Management. Anesthesiology. 2015 Feb;122(2):241-75. [277 references] <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180712211411/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=25545654" target="_blank">PubMed</a> <img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712211411im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712211411/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=49875&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fanesthesiology.pubs.asahq.org%252farticle.aspx%253farticleid%253d2088825">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712211411im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
